OL,3,CKamara on speech problems: 'I buried
OL,4,Cmy head in the sand'
OL,6,FChris Kamara encouraged people not to
OL,7,Fignore health problems as he
OL,8,Fofficially opened a new diagnostic
OL,9,Fcentre in his home city Wakefield.
OL,11,FThe former footballer-turned-pundit
OL,12,Fcut the ribbon at the Community
OL,13,FDiagnostic Centre run by Mid Yorkshire
OL,14,FTeaching NHS Trust at a ceremony on
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,17,FThe facility provides planned
OL,18,Foutpatient tests, including x-rays,
OL,19,Fultrasounds and scans, as well as
OL,20,Fblood, heart and eye tests.
