OL,3,CKamara on speech problems: 'I buried
OL,4,Cmy head in the sand'
OL,6,FIt has already carried out 20,000
OL,7,Fexaminations since informally opening
OL,8,Fin March.
OL,10,FKamara, who revealed he had been
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with speech problems after
OL,12,Fviewers noticed him slurring his words
OL,13,Fon Sky Sports in 2022, said he
OL,14,Finitially put off seeking help.
OL,16,F"I was a big dinosaur," he said. "I
OL,17,Fburied my head in the sand when all
OL,18,Falong I should have been saying
OL,19,F'there's this wrong with me, there's
OL,20,Fthat wrong with me' and when I did it
OL,21,Fchanged my life completely.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
