OL,3,CKamara on speech problems: 'I buried
OL,4,Cmy head in the sand'
OL,6,F"I'm here now enjoying my life, only
OL,7,Fby opening up and talking to people
OL,8,Fand getting my problems diagnosed."
OL,10,FKamara, who is affectionately known to
OL,11,Fmillions as "Kammy", played for Leeds
OL,12,FUnited, Sheffield United and Bradford
OL,13,FCity before becoming a much-loved
OL,14,Fbroadcaster.
OL,16,FHe quit his job with Sky Sports
OL,17,Ffollowing his diagnosis, but has
OL,18,Fcontinued to work in television and
OL,19,Fradio.
