OL,6,FHe said the new centre, at Westgate
OL,7,FRetail Park, would be a boost for
OL,8,Fpeople who were nervous about visiting
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,F"It's the future," he said. "I know a
OL,12,Ffew people who are scared of the
OL,13,Fhospital, so coming to a facility like
OL,14,Fthis is incredible. It makes such a
OL,15,Fdifference."
