OL,6,FThe trust's chief executive, Len
OL,7,FRichards, said: "There is no doubt
OL,8,Fthat it will help more people to
OL,9,Freceive the tests and scans they need
OL,10,Fto speed up the diagnosis of illnesses
OL,11,Flike cancer and heart disease
OL,12,Fultimately helping to improve health
OL,13,Foutcomes for our communities."
